# Liabilities Insurance Participating Business Future Profits Gross Amount

## identifier
de4275

## type
float

## definition
Report the net present value of future Policy Owner Bonuses in relation to future profits for participating business. Current year bonuses are excluded.

Report amounts gross of ceded reinsurance but inclusive of inwards reinsurance.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.Insurance.ParticipatingBusinessFutureProfitsGross.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.04
- period=instant
